$(  \mathbf{5.9})  $ \ Seja $f\in\mathcal{H}(
%TCIMACRO{\U{2102} }%
%BeginExpansion
\mathbb{C}
%EndExpansion
)  $ e suponhamos que \ $f(  z)  =\underset{\left\vert
