z-a)  ^{n+1}}d\lambda=-\underset{n\geq0}{%
%TCIMACRO{\dsum }%
%BeginExpansion
{\displaystyle\sum}
%EndExpansion
}\left\{  \underset{\gamma_{\alpha}}{%
