termo geral da série em

$(  8.8.8)  $ assim $[z\in F$ e $m\in%
%TCIMACRO{\U{2124} }%
%BeginExpansion
\mathbb{Z}
%EndExpansion
_{-}^{\ast}!]:$

\bigskip

$\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \left\vert \dfrac{1}{2\pi i}\underset{\gamma_{\alpha}}{%
%TCIMACRO{\dint }%
%BeginExpansion
{\displaystyle\int}
%EndExpansion
}\dfrac{f(  \lambda)  d\lambda}{(  \lambda-a)  ^{m+1}%
}(  z-a)  ^{m}\right\vert =\dfrac{1}{2\pi}\left\vert \underset
{\gamma_{\sigma}}{%
%TCIMACRO{\dint }%
