_{\gamma_{\sigma}^{\ast}}\cdot(  \dfrac{s_{1}}{\sigma})  ^{m},$
onde $(  \ast)  $ resulta observando que

$z\in F\iff\left\vert z-a\right\vert \geq s_{1}$ e portanto $\left\vert
