i}\underset{\gamma_{\alpha}}{%
%TCIMACRO{\dint }%
%BeginExpansion
{\displaystyle\int}
%EndExpansion
}\dfrac{f(  \lambda)  d\lambda}{(  \lambda-a)  ^{m+1}%
}(  z-a)  ^{m}\right\vert \leq c(  \dfrac{\sigma}{s_{1}%
})  ^{-m}$ \ \ $\forall$ \ $m\in%
%TCIMACRO{\U{2124} }%
%BeginExpansion
\mathbb{Z}
%EndExpansion
_{-}^{\ast}$

e como a série

